Terre_Haute.Duane Yards, Indiana:
Duane Yards is an unincorporated community in Harrison Township, Vigo County, in the U.S. state of Indiana.
Now within the city borders of Terre Haute, it is also part of the Terre Haute metropolitan area.


== Geography ==
Duane Yards is located at 39°29′42″N 87°23′19″W at an elevation of 499 feet.
